Package: helppages
Title: Inspiration for Awesome-Looking R Help Pages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Veerle", "Eeftink - van Leemput", email = "veerle@hypebright.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small demo package showing how to embed custom badges and
    other HTML or SVG fanciness into R function help pages, using the same
    conditional-rendering trick the lifecycle package uses for its stability
    badges. Includes a plain, functional badge family (pipe-friendliness)
    and a purely-for-fun one (Hogwarts house crests) to show what's possible.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
